	<div class="entry"><p>For several years now, Amazon.com has been our go-to service for movie and videogame trade-ins.  Clearing out old stuff in exchange for credit you could spend on pretty much anything was awesome.  New policies and other changes introduced in 2012, however, have caused the quality of the service to deteriorate to the point that we can't really recommend it anymore as of February 2013.  Find out the details here.</p>

