	<div class="entry"><p>The latest entry in the HD collection craze is the Hitman series.  The Hitman HD Trilogy, which actually includes the second, third, and forth games in the series, packs some of the finest pure stealth games ever onto two discs.  Because the Hitman series has evolved so much over time, however, newer fans that came to the series with Absolution or even Blood Money might struggle to overcome the gameplay quirks of the earlier titles, which makes this HD collection a bit tricky to recommend.  We have all of the info here.</p>

